_json.description: The Rose by Bogs Footwear. If Mother Nature had a favorite shoe, this would be it. The Bogs Rose is back and better than ever as the quintessential clog for backyards and sidewalks alike. Built on a European last with a wider toe box and narrower heel for the most comfortable fit. This lightweight slip-on is constructed with 2mm Neo-Tech™ and our Bogs Max-Wick moisture-wicking technology for all-day comfort when out digging in the dirt.
